<div class="authorname columns">
<a href="https://truthout.org/authors/robert-howard/" itemprop="url"><span itemprop="name">Robert Howard</span></a>
</div>
<div class="authorcontent columns" itemprop="description">
<p>Robert Howard is a husband, father, artist and builder in San Francisco, California. He was a juror in the trial of <em>Dwayne Lee Johnson v. Monsanto</em> during the summer of 2018. In October 2018, he wrote and publicly released a letter to the judge in that case protesting her tentative ruling to toss the jury&rsquo;s verdict. Four other jurors followed suit.</p>
